2011-05-06T06:09:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-06/horizon-secs-co-april-sales-fall-53-90-table-6015-tt.html
HORIZON SECS CO said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 53.90% to NT$45,006,000 from NT$97,618,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2011           4/2010
Sales             45,006           97,618    
YOY%             -53.90%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            243,739          280,554    
YOY%             -13.12% 
=================================================================
 